metadata.name: Doge Rubiks Cube
metadata.description:
Support Dogecoin and show off this 3D Puzzle NFT. 
All NFTs come with a file of textures and the models.
This will give you the ability to use your NFT in the Metaverse. Imagen solving your puzzle in VR...

                                               Dogecoin To The Moon
                                                                      Nathan Simers
